Package: brittnu
Title: Britt's Nu for Dirichlet-Distributed Data
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: 
    person(given = "Brian",
           family = "Britt",
           role = c("aut", "cre"),
           email = "bcbritt@ua.edu",
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0002-1521-3258"))
Description: This function computes the Britt's nu reliability coefficient for
    data sets composed of multiple Dirichlet-distributed deviates with at least
    two categories. This is especially useful to assess the reliability of
    cross-validations of latent Dirichlet allocation.
